Package tmiranda.mus

Class Summary
API This class presents methods that can be invoked from within the Sage STV to perform all of the tasks necessary to implement the Multi-User Plugin.
DelimitedString DelimitedString is a class that allows manipulation of Strings containing data separated by a delimiter.
Log Logging methods.
MultiAiring Class that implements the SageTV AiringAPI for multiple users.
MultiFavorite Class that implements the SageTV FavoriteAPI for multiple users.
MultiMediaFile Class that implements the SageTV MediaFileAPI for multiple users.
MultiObject Class that implements many of the methods needed for MultiMediaFiles, MultiAirings and MultiFavorites.
Plugin This is the Plugin Implementation Class for a SageTV Plugin.
SageUtil Class containing useful utilities.
User Class that implements the user related functionality.
